Package: ResidualPlot
Title: Residual Plot for simple linear models 
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nat", "MacMillan", , "nmac2000@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package creates a resiudal plot using the "lm" function to make the model and "ggplot2" to make the graph. The plot has the fitted results in the x axis and the residuals on the y axis.
